data.description: This recently renovated semi-detached home with 4 bedrooms and 1 bathroom offers plenty of space with room to grow. It features a new kitchen with stainless steel appliance and newly renovated bathroom. The spacious living room and dining room, along with the beautiful hardwood floors and recessed lighting, create a welcoming and stylish atmosphere. You'll also enjoy the comfort of central air and forced hot air heating, ensuring a cozy living environment year-round. The basement is clean and offers the potential to install a second bathroom, providing even more convenience. The plumbing and electric systems have been recently updated, giving you peace of mind. Located in the wonderful town of Kenilworth, you'll have easy access to the Garden State Parkway, Cranford & Union Train Stations, Nomahegan Park, Kean University, and Newark Airport. Just unpack your bags and start enjoying all that this home and the surrounding area have to offer!
